[00:00.00]Teeth - 5 Seconds Of Summer
[00:02.32]Lyrics by：Louis Bell/Luke Hemmings/Ashton Irwin/Ali Tamposi/Ryan Tedder/Andrew Wotman/Stephen Morris/Bernard Sumner/Peter Hook/Gillian Gilbert/Evan Rogers/Carl Sturken
