[00:06.97]Some days you're the only thing I know
{"曾经 你就是我的全部"}
[00:10.43]Only thing that's burning when the nights grow cold
{"孤独寒夜里唯一的慰藉"}
[00:13.64]Can't look away can't look away
{"眼里全是你"}
[00:17.29]Beg you to stay beg you to stay yeah
{"求你不要走"}
[00:20.69]Sometimes you're a stranger in my bed
{"有时候 你像是与我同床共枕的陌生人"}
[00:24.05]Don't know if you love me or you want me dead
{"不知道你是爱我还是想要我的命"}
[00:27.51]Push me away push me away
{"将我推开"}
[00:30.86]Then beg me to stay beg me to stay yeah
{"又求我不要走"}
[00:34.54]Call me in the morning to apologize
{"早上给我打电话道歉"}
[00:38.04]Every little lie gives me butterflies
{"每一个谎言都让我心花怒放"}
[00:41.35]Something in the way you're looking through my eyes
{"你看我的眼神有一种说不清楚的感觉"}
[00:44.81]Don't know if I'm gonna make it out alive
{"不知道我能否撑下去"}
[00:48.25]Fight so dirty but your love's so sweet
{"争吵得如此激烈 但你的爱如此甜蜜"}
[00:51.72]Talk so pretty but your heart got teeth
{"甜言蜜语如此动听 但你的心上长了獠牙"}
[00:55.27]Late night devil put your hands on me
{"深夜的恶魔 对我痛下毒手"}
[00:58.61]And never never never ever let go
{"我却始终不愿放手"}
